Articles.Content:
I build lots of landers.. Manned, Unmanned, Rovers, Sky-Cranes, etc..

Looking for some landing legs.. Pretty bored with stock or any of the ones that

come with many of the major mods.. I see some in various images that I have no clue

where they get them.. Believe me, I have searched and searched endlessly..

Anyone know of anything rare, cool, unique or hardly known as far as landing legs/struts are concerned??

Not looking for wheeled landing gear..

Thanks in advance and I hope this was the right section of the forum to post in..

Live long and Prosper....
AIES aerospace has some very nice ones.
